Uses of Package
com.tailf.navu

  • Packages that use com.tailf.navu 
    Package Description
    com.tailf.dp
    Data provider API package, for implementation of callbacks for validations, actions, transformation etc.
    com.tailf.dp.annotations
    Annotations and proxy helper classes for callbacks.
    com.tailf.dp.services
    Service callback specific context and utilities.
    com.tailf.navu
    NAVU (Navigation Utilities) is an API which provides increased accessibility to the ConfD/NCS populated data model tree: NAVU-Tree.
    com.tailf.navu.traversal
    Utility package for traversing the NAVU tree using NAVU API.

    This interface specifies minimum requirement that a element in NAVU implements.

  • Classes in com.tailf.navu used by com.tailf.navu 
    Class and Description
    AbstractNavuNode
    This class provides a skeleton implementation of the NavuNode interface, to minimize the effort required to implement this interface.
    IterationEntry
    This class represents a iteration summary from a completed iteration.
    NavuAction
    This class represents a action modeled in the data model.
    NavuCdbConfigDiffIterate
    This interface specifies the method to implement to be able to react on CDB configuration changes.
    NavuCdbConfigSubscriber
    CDB Configurational data subscriber which handles user callbacks that implements NavuCdbConfigIterate.
    NavuCdbDiffIterate
    This interface specifies the interface to be fulfilled by a CDB subscriber callback.
    NavuCdbOperDiffIterate
    This interface specifies the method to implement to be able to react on CDB operational changes.
    NavuCdbStoppedHandler
    This interface specifies method subscriberStop which will be called before the subscriber is stopped.
    NavuCdbSubscriber
    This interface declares common methods that is mostly implemented by the abstract class NavuCdbSubscribers.
    NavuCdbSubscribers
    This class provides general base implementation to the NavuCdbSubscriber interface.
    NavuCdbSubscriptionConfigContext
    This interface specifies additional method for retrieve the old value of a leaf for a CDB change entry on a change set.
    NavuCdbSubscriptionContext
    This interface specifies the interface for retrieving information for a CDB change entry on a change set.
    NavuCdbSubscriptionIterQueue 
    NavuCdbSubscriptionOperContext
    This interface specifies the interface for retrieving information for a CDB change entry on a change set.
    NavuCdbSubscriptionTwoPhaseContext 
    NavuChange
    This class handles changes on a node.
    NavuChoice
    This class handles Yang presentation and setting of Yang choices.
    NavuContainer
    NavuContainer is a representation of the yang construct container,module and list-entry.
    NavuContext
    This class abstracts the means of how NAVU should populates its tree.
    NavuContext.UnSetCaseInChoice
    The enumeration specifies the behavior when a case in a choice is not selected explicitly or implicitly.
    NavuException
    Exception raised from the navu package
    NavuLeaf
    The NavuLeaf class corresponding to the Yang leaf and leaf-list node types.
    NavuList
    NavuList is a representation of the yang list node.
    NavuList.WhereTo 
    NavuNode
    This interface specifies minimum requirement that a element in NAVU implements.
    NavuNodeInfo
    This class contains meta information for a node.
    NavuNodeSetIterate
    This class is used by AbstractNavuNode.xPathSelectIterate(String, NavuNodeSetIterate) The iterate method is called for each node iteration.
    NavuXPathContext
    This class contains Node context for a callback iterator implementing NavuNodeSetIterate which is used by AbstractNavuNode.xPathSelectIterate(String, NavuNodeSetIterate)
    PreparedXMLStatement
    This class represent a pre-parsable object of a parsed XML-string.
